          "AdditionalTradeItemDescription": [
            {
              "LanguageCode": "en",
              "Value": "Absorbent wound dressing is highly absorbent, consists of nonwoven, high-absorbent fabric  and PE net film\nThe wound contact layer of one side direction PE net film does not stick to the surface of a wound or cause trauma to delicate new tissue when removal. The core of the dressing is high-absorbent fabric and polyurethane foam which can absorb the exudates continuously, lock exudate into the product, preventing the wound bed from drying out and the surrounding skin from becoming macerated, so as to promote accelerated wound healing. It is soft and comfortable. It has good compliance to the body and has good cushioning to release pressure.                                                                                size:10cm * 15cm"
